WEBVTT

00:00:00.437 --> 00:00:02.254
Track 12.01

00:00:04.107 --> 00:00:04.884
Narrator: 1

00:00:06.021 --> 00:00:08.100
A: Is there an email from Stephen?

00:00:08.859 --> 00:00:10.518
He’s going to write to you with

00:00:10.543 --> 00:00:12.359
information about the boat trip.

00:00:12.384 --> 00:00:17.405
B: I don’t know. I’m not going to check my emails today or tomorrow.

00:00:17.430 --> 00:00:19.169
A: Oh, OK.

00:00:19.806 --> 00:00:22.298
Well, I’m going to phone him this evening,

00:00:22.323 --> 00:00:24.063
so I can ask him then.

00:00:25.941 --> 00:00:26.902
Narrator: 2

00:00:27.616 --> 00:00:29.640
A: It’s the holidays!

00:00:29.665 --> 00:00:33.270
I’m going to sleep for ten hours every night!

00:00:33.295 --> 00:00:36.407
I’m going to watch TV every day!

00:00:36.432 --> 00:00:39.985
B: Really? That’s so boring!

00:00:40.010 --> 00:00:44.274
My brother and I are going to work on a farm near the mountains.

00:00:44.299 --> 00:00:47.992
The people there are going to teach us how to ride horses.

00:00:48.017 --> 00:00:50.607
A: Hmm, sounds quite interesting.

00:00:51.355 --> 00:00:52.689
What about your sister?

00:00:52.714 --> 00:00:54.849
B: She isn’t going to come with us.

00:00:54.874 --> 00:00:56.905
She wants to stay at home.